NAME
    Catalyst::Plugin::Upload::Basename - Basename for uploads

SYNOPSIS
        use Catalyst qw[Upload::Basename];

        if ( my $upload = $c->request->upload('field') ) {
            print $upload->basename;
        }

DESCRIPTION
    Extends "Catalyst::Request::Upload" with a basename method.

METHODS
    basename
        Returns basename for "filename".

SEE ALSO
    Catalyst::Request, Catalyst::Request::Upload.

AUTHOR
    Christian Hansen, "ch@ngmedia.com"

